{"tid":1605164,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"以航拍機投擲爆炸品 美國男子被 FBI 扣查","createTime":"2019-09-30T07:52:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T15:07:37.000Z","uid":133727,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"8d6d6b21caf1a08987831004c4595266cf3b079b","tid":1605164,"uid":133727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T07:52:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2019/09/20/man-accused-of-using-drone-to-airdrop-explosives/life-tech/drone/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2019%2F09%2F20%2Fman-accused-of-using-drone-to-airdrop-explosives%2Flife-tech%2Fdrone%2F&d=l0hx0y7EoyLX%2BzZhnd86ZkBo7c%2BYFxEppcXi0rJe94o%3D&h=883b4753\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2019/09/20/man-accused-of-using-drone-to-airdrop-explosives/life-tech/drone/</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>以航拍機投擲爆炸品 美國男子被 FBI 扣查</strong><br />\n<br />\n美國賓夕法尼亞州檢控人員，日前指汽車技工 Jason Muzzicato 利用航拍機，空投炸彈到前女友的家。Muzzicato 今年 6 月初被 FBI 拘捕，在搜查他的工作地點和住處，搜出了 10 把槍，當中包括半自動手槍和 AR-15 步槍，還有 7 枚人手製作爆炸品。由於 Muzzicato 在 2017 年曾經犯下家庭暴力罪行，所以他被禁止擁有槍械。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nMuzzicato 日前因為非法擁有槍械和爆炸品，還有未經註冊情況下使用 DJI Phantom 3 航拍機而被起訴。<span style=\"color: red;\">檢控官指 Muzzicato 利用航拍機運送爆炸品到前女友的物業，案情非常嚴重</span>，所以需要繼續監禁，不准許對方申請保釋。<span style=\"color: red;\">法院亦表示只要將搜到的非法槍械、爆炸品和航拍機加起來，就知道想像到可能出現的傷害有幾大。</span><br />\n<br />\n不過 Muzzicato 的辯護律師指，其客戶否認曾經使用航拍機空投炸彈。FBI 則表示正在分析 Muzzicato 的手機，試圖找出航拍機的使用時間和飛行路線。<span style=\"color: red;\">有當地市民指曾經聽到爆炸聲，而家用閉路電視亦拍攝到爆炸情況，市民表示當時附近無人，爆炸物是從天而降的。</span><br />\n<br />\n來源：gizmodo"},{"pid":"9467ac57e3444d13b439ace31c3f59ed00cbd18f","tid":1605164,"uid":84538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T07:53:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"488b2ff71238ddeddbb858392985c35dd8c399d2","tid":1605164,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T07:54:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c041d0a30c401bbc40da342f95de9792e0b82fb2","tid":1605164,"uid":133727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T07:55:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9023fb7dca7c0d58554d241a726a1da2803af96b","tid":1605164,"uid":133727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T07:56:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a0b7436dc421df34896e1734bc7e55c005fff5a5","tid":1605164,"uid":76098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T07:57:44.000Z","msg":"用咩類型炸彈🤔"},{"pid":"f429a7e04704c85232af21c5b2c9f9ec06f69dc0","tid":1605164,"uid":133727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a0b7436dc421df34896e1734bc7e55c005fff5a5","tid":1605164,"uid":76098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T07:57:44.000Z","msg":"用咩類型炸彈🤔"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T08:00:36.000Z","msg":"可能係氣油彈"},{"pid":"d6f5d28cfc65eca732f96eafdf8e1881eb0ab595","tid":1605164,"uid":133727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T08:03:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bbeb578e795e2d43063f1d784e03bd727da540d3","tid":1605164,"uid":133727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T08:05:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fd734de2200821bf55f14b91f4f5b3333bf8caf9","tid":1605164,"uid":197121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T08:06:05.000Z","msg":"千其唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bda929610a86495d48e2c5b244296dd9c73a1614","tid":1605164,"uid":286206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T08:11:38.000Z","msg":"教訓你地用要用發夢手機玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b3ef9968a89edcd0dc45d38b8f5e31e9f71e1fc","tid":1605164,"uid":266011,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T09:31:47.000Z","msg":"有冇睇天使淪陷，佢直頭係無人機自爆式攻擊"},{"pid":"e9b55d2c085e527f299fadbd938ef5bdf8c5bfc1","tid":1605164,"uid":133727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"c